IMAPStore migadu-alx-remote
Host imap.migadu.com
Port 993
User alx@alejandro-colomar.es
PassCmd "pass show email/migadu/alx/mailbox/alx/pass"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

MaildirStore migadu-alx-local
Path ~/mail/migadu/alx/
Inbox ~/mail/migadu/alx/Inbox
SubFolders Verbatim

Channel migadu-alx
Far :migadu-alx-remote:
Near :migadu-alx-local:
Create Both
Expunge Both
Patterns *
SyncState *

IMAPStore gmail-remote
Host imap.gmail.com
Port 993
User alx.manpages
PassCmd "pass show email/gmail/alx.manpages/imap"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

MaildirStore gmail-local
Path ~/mail/gmail/alx/
Inbox ~/mail/gmail/alx/INBOX
SubFolders Verbatim

Channel gmail
Far :gmail-remote:
Near :gmail-local:
Create Both
Expunge Both
Patterns *
SyncState *
